products.title: Santa Fe Eggshell (Matt)
products.metadescription: Buy made to measure Santa Fe Eggshell (Matt) Wooden Venetian Blinds from SoEasy Blinds. Order quality Wooden Venetian Blinds online today at low prices with fast UK delivery
products.productdescription:
Min Width: 305mm Max Width: 2896mm
 	Min Drop: 305mm Max Drop: 3500mm
 	Slat Composition: Basswood
 	Slat Widths Available: 50mm

 	Pelmet: Co-ordinating pelmet
 	Headrail: Robust aluminium headrail 51mm wide x 57mm deep.
